OL,3,CNeighbour smelt gas weeks before fatal
OL,4,CMorriston house explosion, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe next door neighbour of a man who
OL,8,Fdied in a large house explosion smelt
OL,9,Fgas in the weeks before, an inquest
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FBrian Davies, 68, was killed in the
OL,13,Fincident on March 13 2023 when his
OL,14,Fhome on Clydach Road, Morriston,
OL,15,FSwansea, was destroyed in the blast
OL,16,Fsending debris across the road and
OL,17,Fnearby streets.
