OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FCCTV footage from a nearby house was
OL,8,Fplayed which showed postman Jonathan
OL,9,FRoberts driving up Clydach Road when
OL,10,Fthe blast covered his van in debris.
OL,12,FClaire Bennett, who lived next door to
OL,13,FMr Davies, was injured in the
OL,14,Fexplosion and had to be rescued from
OL,15,Fher home.
