OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FShe told an inquest in Swansea that
OL,8,Fshe had been smelling gas at the rear
OL,9,Fof her property for the previous few
OL,10,Fweeks, which she attributed to
OL,11,Fmaintenance work being carried out at
OL,12,Fa nearby house.
OL,14,FOn the day of the explosion, she had
OL,15,Ftaken her daughter to school and was
OL,16,Fsitting in her lounge when she heard a
OL,17,Floud bang.
