OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"There was a massive bang, and I
OL,8,Fimmediately thought a car had hit the
OL,9,Ffront corner of the house," she told
OL,10,Fthe hearing.
OL,12,F"Things went dark and I lost a couple
OL,13,Fof seconds and came to. The house was
OL,14,Ffilled with debris and the ceiling and
OL,15,Fwalls had fallen in.
OL,17,F"I remember a gentleman's voice saying
OL,18,Fto me, 'It's okay'. I just remember he
OL,19,Fwas pulling loads of debris off me to
OL,20,Fget me off the sofa.
