OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"Brian's house was completely
OL,8,Fdestroyed and at first they didn't
OL,9,Fknow there was a house there."
OL,11,FShe said before the incident she had
OL,12,Fbeen smelling gas at the rear of her
OL,13,Fhome.
OL,15,F"For about a fortnight I would go out
OL,16,Fthrough the side gate and there was a
OL,17,Fsmell of gas ` really strong in the
OL,18,Froad," she said.
