OL,4,CMorriston house explosion, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"At the time the house opposite the
OL,8,Fclose was having work done and I just
OL,9,Fthought the smell was them doing work."
OL,11,FMs Bennett said her home was destroyed
OL,12,Fin the explosion and she had lost many
OL,13,Fof her possessions and was now
OL,14,Fundergoing counselling for PTSD.
OL,16,F"For about a year-and-a-half from the
OL,17,Fmoment I open my eyes in the morning
OL,18,Funtil I go to bed at night, I thought
OL,19,FI was going to die," she added.
