OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"Things are triggering, like the dark
OL,8,Fand noises."
OL,10,FAt the beginning of the inquest Aled
OL,11,FWyn Gruffydd, senior coroner for
OL,12,FSwansea and Neath Port Talbot, told
OL,13,Fthe jury they would hear evidence of
OL,14,Fhow Mr Davies died in the explosion
OL,15,F"as well as the circumstances of that
OL,16,Fexplosion".
