OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe inquest heard the grandfather-of-
OL,8,Fthree, who worked in the construction
OL,9,Findustry, had rented the one-bedroom
OL,10,Fend of terrace property for about four
OL,11,Fyears before his death.
OL,13,FWales and West Utilities, which
OL,14,Fmaintains the gas network across Wales
OL,15,Fand the south-west of England, is
OL,16,Frepresented during the inquest, and
OL,17,Fthe Health and Safety Executive is
OL,18,Falso in attendance.
OL,20,FThe inquest, which is due to last a
OL,21,Fweek at Swansea Guildhall, continues.
